existing logical drive. The technical specialist advises that hard drives need to be added to
the array group first to provide the capacity to do the update.
What operations are performed within the DS3524 operating system to achieve the
upgrade?
A. Dynamic RAID migration
B. Dynamic Array Expansion only
C. Dynamic Volume Expansion only
D. Dynamic Array Expansion and then Dynamic Volume Expansion
Answer: D

low cost device to achieve the necessary cost benefit. While a tape library solution would
provide low cost, the customer application is not capable of writing directly to tape.

application to access tape devices?
A. Implement IBM LTFS Library Edition using LTO-5orTS1140 tape drives in the library
B. Implement SAN Volume Controller with LTFS enabled, allowing IBM LTO drives to act

C. Implement IBM LTFS Single Drive Edition on all IBM-supplied LTO-4 or LTO-5 drives in

D. Implement ProtecTIER with LTFS, allowing the management of tape and VTL disk under
